Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.61,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,Let us destroy one another
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:32.78,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,And face the ending full of mystery that lies ahead
