Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:40.11,OP_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{an3}{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,3400,3600)}虚空の中　朽ち果てるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.02,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,There is another me
